      <title>埃利奥特在零售商冷落后结束了库里的收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/elliott-walks-away-from-making-fresh-offer-for-uk-s-currys</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃利奥特投资管理公司(Elliott Investment Management)放弃了对Currys Plc的潜在收购，导致这家英国电子零售商的股价暴跌，并为中国京东公司(JD.com Inc.)可能的收购铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/elliott-walks-away-from-making-fresh-offer-for-uk-s-currys</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:22:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀倒计时开始，美国期货下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/asian-stocks-to-fall-as-us-cpi-shifts-into-focus-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股指期货在数据密集的一周开始后表现不佳，随后美国通胀的重要报告将测试牛市的决心，押注美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔和他的同事们正在接近转向更宽松的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/asian-stocks-to-fall-as-us-cpi-shifts-into-focus-markets-wrap</guid>
